      ]
    ],
    "rationale": "Reorder the index by the ESR rule (Equality['storeLocation'] -> Sort['saleDate'] -> Range['customer.age']). With Sort placed before Range, the index yields documents already in sort order, removing the blocking SORT stage and the over-scan it causes."
